The '''Public Safety Commission''' was an organization that was responsible for medical and emergency crisis response on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Chandrila/Legends|Chandrila]]. As of [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], the organization had 575 employees. That year, in response to the vote to form the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]], the employees, among whom was [[Ocandra Leeds]], who believed this would depersonalize their services, walked off the job for 48 standard hours in protest.

